      :
      <b>
       wsh yr bwl
      </b>
     </h2>
     <div class="entry">
      <p>
       Thr’s
       <a href="http://www.nozen.com/washbowl.htm">
        fms Zn stry
       </a>
       tht gs:
      </p>
      <blockquote>
       <p>
        A mnk tld Jsh, “I hv jst ntrd th mnstry. Pls tch m.”
        <br/>
        Jsh skd, “Hv y tn yr rc prrdg?
        <br/>
        Th mnk rpld, “I hv tn.”
        <br/>
        Jsh sd, “Thn y hd bttr wsh yr bwl.”
        <br/>
        At tht mmnt th mnk ws nlghtnd.
       </p>
      </blockquote>
      <p>
       I’m nt gng t try t xpln tht stry, s I m fr frm nlghtnd ngh t ndrstnd t. Instd, I’d lk t fcs th wndrfl smplcty f tht dvc:
      </p>
      <blockquote>
       <p>
        Hv y tn yr rc prrdg? Thn y hd bttr wsh yr bwl.
        <span id="more-594">
        </span>
       </p>
      </blockquote>
      <p>
       Ths s smthng I thnk f vry tm I t, nd n fct whnvr I’m dn dng smthng. “Dn tng? Thn wsh yr bwl.”
      </p>
      <p>
       Thr s smthng prfnd nd yt mnmlst bt ths dvc. It’s: dn’t gt yr hd cght p n ll ths thnkng bt th mnng f lf … nstd, jst d. Jst wsh yr bwl. And n th wshng, y’ll fnd ll y nd.
      </p>
      <p>
       I’v fnd ths t b tr. I ltrlly wsh my bwl ftr tng, slwly nd wth mndflnss. It’s stsfyng, nd tks n mny nd lttl rsrcs.
      </p>
      <p>
       Whn I tk  shwr, I hnd wsh my drty clths (f thy’r drty), wrng thm t, hng thm t dry. Whn I chng, I crflly pt wy th clths I’v chngd t f. Whn I prpr fd, I wp th cntr nd pt wy th ngrdnts. At lst I try t – I dn’t clm t b prfct.
      </p>
      <p>
       Rmmbrng t d ths thngs whn w’r dn wth th ctvty sn’t jst bt ntnss. It’s bt mndflnss, bt cmpltng wht w strtd, bt bng prsnt n ll w d nstd f rshng t th nxt ctvty.
      </p>
      <p>
       Wsh yr bwl, wth cr nd jy.
      </p>
